Passive.Name: Son of K'un-Lun
Passive.Description:

On Turn, 40% chance to heal self and __Defender__ allies for 30% of this character's Max Health, and heal additional __City__ __Hero__ allies for 20% of this character's Max Health.
Gain +5% damage for each __Defender__ ally.

Passive.Name: Stark Upgrades

Basic.Name: Jaw Breaker

Attack primary target for 220% damage + 50% chance to Bonus attack 1-2 times for 170% damage.
Generate 1 Ability Energy for a random __Defender__ ally. Each attack has a 50% chance to generate 1 Ability Energy for a random ally.

Special.Name: Shake it Off
Special.Description:
Clear all negative effects from self and all allies.
Generate 1 Ability Energy for each __Defender__ ally. Generate 4 Ability Energy for random allies.

Ultimate.Name: Rejection

Attack primary target for 400% damage + clear all positive effects.

Passive.Name: Denial
Passive.Description:
Gain +40% Resistance.
__Defender__ allies gain +40% Resistance.
Additional __City__ allies gain +20% Resistance.
Other additional allies gain +15% Resistance.

This attack cannot be blocked.

Gain **Taunt** + **Defense Up** for 2 turns + **Immunity** + **Deathproof** + 2 **Regeneration**.
If Magneto is an ally, gain **Taunt** for 2 turns.

Ultimate.Name: Crushing Charge
Ultimate.Description:
Attack primary and adjacent targets for 380% damage. Damage is increased by 80% per **Charged**.
This attack cannot be blocked.

Passive.Name: I'm the Juggernaut!
Passive.Description:
On Turn, gain **Charged**, up to a maximum of 4. On Spawn, clear all but one stack of **Charged**. If any **Charged** were cleared, fill Speed Bar by 40%.
If Magneto is an ally, when an enemy attacks this character, fill Speed Bar by 20%.
Gain +5% Max Health
Gain +10% Resistance
Gain +1000% Resistance while he has **Immunity**.
Gain +1000% Resistance against **Stun**.

Basic.Description: Attack primary target for 330% damage + 30% Drain. On Crit, Bonus Attack 2 times for 330% damage + 30% Drain and lose **Charged**. Otherwise, gain +1 **Charged** up to a maximum of 5.

Special.Description: Attack primary target for 200% damage 3 times. On Crit, gain **Offense Up** and lose **Charged**. Otherwise, gain +1 **Charged** up to a maximum of 5.

Ultimate.Name: Battle Frenzy
Ultimate.Description:
Attack primary target for 300% damage. Chain to all adjacent targets for 240% damage.
On Crit, attack all enemies for 200% damage and lose **Charged**. Otherwise, gain +1 **Charged** up to a maximum of 5.
**Counterattack** breaks this Chain.

On Kill, heal for 10% of this character's Max Health.

Whenever this character or an ally gains energy, heal them for 2000 Health + 5% of this character's Max Health.
If that target is Ronan or a __Kree__ __Minion__, heal them for 4000 Health + 10% of this character's Max Health.

If __Ronan__ is an ally, heal for an additional 1850 Health + 10% of Max Health.

Gain **Taunt** for 2 turns + 2 **Regeneration**. Clear all negative effects from self.
Apply **Regeneration** to all __Defender__ allies.

Gain **Defense Up** for 2 turns + **Deathproof**.
Apply **Defense Up** to all __Defender__ allies for 2 turns. Apply **Defense Up** to all additional allies. Generate 1 - 3 Ability Energy for random allies.

+15% Max Health.
